<S ID="102473">
8
</S>
<S ID="102684">
Mon collègue préférerait écarter ces éléments de preuve en vertu du   par. 24(2) pour le motif que, «n'eût été» la violation de l'al. 10b), la police n'aurait   certainement pas découvert l'arme du crime.
