<S ID="119448">
voir A.   W. Bryant, M. Gold, H. M. Stevenson et D. Northrup, «Public Attitudes Toward the   Exclusion of Evidence:  Section 24(2) of the Canadian Charter of Rights and   Freedoms» (1990), 69 R. du B. can. 1, et «Public Support for the Exclusion of   Unconstitutionally Obtained Evidence» (1990), 1 S.C.L.R. (2d) 555.
